      "check:domain-boundaries unless its exact { file, specifier } pair is on the `exemptFiles` migration",
      "allowlist below. This inverts the prior `enforcedFiles` opt-in model — new code now fails closed and",
      "must import a stable subpath (e.g. @dzupagent/core/runtime) or earn a time-boxed exemption.",
      "Every exemption MUST carry an `owner` (team/codeowner) and an `expiryVersion` (the release by which the",
      "import is migrated off the broad root). Shrink this list; do not grow it."
    ],
